VS Test step
1. when you want to test unit function ,so you can do this.
   a.right click in the code where cusor in public class or public function.
   b.when in public class ,it will pop up a dialog and set it ,you can in a new /old file add all test functions in this class.
   c.when in public function,it has the same operation ,but only add a function in which your cursor click.
